snippet.title: Amber Heard Faces 10 Years In Prison For Pocketing Charity Donations From Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Faces 10 Years In Prison For Pocketing Charity Donations From Johnny Depp
One of the ongoing things about the case between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard is the fact that the two are calling out everything the two have done in the far past or recent past. Nothing is off the table and everything regards to trying to win the case against one another. Amber Heard has been going after Johnny’s antics in movies And now, Johnny is pulling out something from her past and using it big-time against her. We’ll break it down for you.
